SIMPLE: until
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Until
<hw>Un*til"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prep.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>until</ets>, <ets>ontil</ets>; <ets>un-</ets> (as in
<ets>unto</ets>) + <ets>til</ets> till; cf. Dan. <ets>indtil</ets>, Sw.
<ets>intill</ets>. See <er>Unto</er>, and <er>Till</er>,
<pos>prep.</pos>]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>To; unto; towards; -- used of material
objects.</def> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Taverners <qex>until</qex> them told the same.</q> <rj><qau>Piers
Plowman.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He roused himself full blithe, and hastened them
<qex>until</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Spenser.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To; up to; till; before; -- used of time; <as>as, he
staid <ex>until</ex> evening; he will not come back <ex>until</ex> the
end of the month</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He and his sons were priests to the tribe of Dan <qex>until</qex>
the day of the captivity.</q> <rj><qau>Judg. xviii. 30.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ In contracts and like documents <xex>until</xex> is
construed as exclusive of the date mentioned unless it was the manifest
intent of the parties to include it.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Until</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Until
<hw>Un*til"</hw>, <pos>conj.</pos> <def>As far as; to the place or
degree that; especially, up to the time that; till. See <er>Till</er>,
<pos>conj.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>In open prospect nothing bounds our eye,⟦br⟧
<qex>Until</qex> the earth seems joined unto the sky.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>But the rest of the dead lives not again <qex>until</qex> the
thousand years were finished.</q> <rj><qau>Rev. xx. 5.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Untile</ent>⟦br⟧
